data.description: Well maintained, clean ranch home offering 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths with 856 sq ft of living space. Eat-in kitchen with appliances, good sized living room opening into front sunroom, 2 bedrooms and full bath make up the main level. Full basement with full bath and potential for optional living space. Laundry area and plenty of storage. Outside features a single-car garage with a covered side patio, a fenced-in backyard, and a good-sized deck directly outside the back door. Nice easy keeper home, don't miss out! Call for private showings.
